title: Bunch of Heroes complete (working online!)
description:
================================================================================
Bunch of Heroes
================================================================================

English


================================================================================
About this Jimbus edition:
================================================================================

- Updated with the latest patch.
- The game is complete. Nothing has been deleted.
- Halloween DLC and the Holiday Pack are included.
- It includes the libraries the game requires.
- Multiplayer works using Steam.


================================================================================
Instructions:
================================================================================

1. IMPORTANT! Install Steam.
2. Run the .exe file to install the game.
3. Use the shortcuts the installer creates.


================================================================================
FAQ:
================================================================================

Q: Does the multiplayer work?
A: Yes, it does.

Q: Do I need Steam to play?
A: Not at all.


Q: Does it work under Windows 10?
A: Yes, it does.

Q: Is this a Jimbus edition?
A: No, it is not. 



Notice this is not an update but the full game. Do not install it over an existing installation
